data.description:
Welcome to Hamilton Green in the vibrant southwest area of Charlotte! This exceptional one-owner home is a spacious 6-bedroom, 3 ½ bathroom haven, perfect for family living and entertaining. As you enter, you'll be greeted by a grand 2-story foyer that sets the tone for the entire home. The well-lit art niche is the perfect place to showcase your favorite artwork, making a lasting impression on your guests from the moment they arrive.
The main floor boasts a versatile formal living and dining room area, which could also serve as a home office for added convenience. The primary bedroom and bathroom on the main floor provide ease and comfort, while the additional 5 bedrooms upstairs, including one with an en-suite bathroom currently used as a media room, offer flexibility and ample space for a growing family or guests. The recently updated kitchen features beautiful white granite countertops and a double oven, ideal for both entertaining and family gatherings.
